homesites.overview: The Great Room and kitchen share a convenient open floorplan on the first floor of this two-story home, with sliding glass doors that lead to the lanai. All three bedrooms occupy the second level, including the  owner’s suite which is comprised of a restful bedroom, en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet.

This comfortable two-story home features an open-concept design combining the Great Room, kitchen and dining room, with an attached lanai for seamless everyday living. Upstairs, a cozy loft area is surrounded by two secondary bedrooms and an expansive owner’s suite, complete with an en-suite bathroom and oversized closet.

This new two-story home showcases a pleasing, contemporary design. The first floor features a large entry and an open floorplan among the modern kitchen, tranquil dining room and inviting family room. The laundry room is located by the kitchen, and a lanai is tucked beside the family room. Upstairs, three bedrooms including a lavish owner’s suite provide restful retreats for family members and guests.
